  "content": "<div dir=\"auto\" class=\"body markup\"><blockquote><p><span>An update on </span><a href=\"https://www.treeverse.net/\" rel=\"\">Treeverse</a><span>. A look at our development and art team progress. We will be posting monthly for you to follow along the development of </span><a href=\"https://www.treeverse.net/\" rel=\"\">Treeverse</a><span>, so make sure you subscribe!</span></p></blockquote><div data-component-name=\"SubscribeWidget\" class=\"subscribe-widget\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-justifyContent-center pc-reset\"><div class=\"container-IpPqBD\"><form action=\"/api/v1/free?nojs=true\" method=\"post\" class=\"form form-M5sC90\" novalidate=\"\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_url\" value=\"https://endlessclouds.substack.com/p/end-claim-is-now-live\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_referrer\" value=\"\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"current_url\" value=\"https://endlessclouds.substack.com/p/monthly-treeverse-update-20\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"current_referrer\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_session_url\" value=\"https://endlessclouds.substack.com/p/monthly-treeverse-update-20\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"first_session_referrer\" value=\"\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"referral_code\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"source\" value=\"subscribe-widget\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"referring_pub_id\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"additional_referring_pub_ids\"><div class=\"sideBySideWrap-vGXrwP\"><div class=\"emailInputWrapper-QlA86j\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-minWidth-0 pc-position-relative flexAuto-Bzdrdy pc-reset\"><input name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Type your email...\" type=\"email\" class=\"pencraft emailInput-OkIMeB input-y4v6N4 inputText-pV_yWb\"></div></div><button type=\"submit\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft rightButton primary subscribe-btn button-VFSdkv buttonBase-GK1x3M\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"button-text \">Subscribe</span></button></div><div id=\"error-container\"></div></form><div class=\"animationWrapper-QRL6aQ\"></div></div></div></div><div><hr></div><p>Gm! Big 20. ICYMI, we just announced what was in the box… and it’s a dinosaur from Capsule Heroes! Check it out.</p><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!DoK6!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa746a8ad-25d0-43b5-93ee-34ffcc7fea7e_583x440.png\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" rel=\"\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!DoK6!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa746a8ad-25d0-43b5-93ee-34ffcc7fea7e_583x440.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!DoK6!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa746a8ad-25d0-43b5-93ee-34ffcc7fea7e_583x440.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!DoK6!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa746a8ad-25d0-43b5-93ee-34ffcc7fea7e_583x440.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!DoK6!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa746a8ad-25d0-43b5-93ee-34ffcc7fea7e_583x440.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!DoK6!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fa746a8ad-25d0-43b5-93ee-34ffcc7fea7e_583x440.png\" width=\"583\" height=\"440\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/a746a8ad-25d0-43b5-93ee-34ffcc7fea7e_583x440.png&quot;,&quot;src