 16\"></path><path d=\"M8 16H3v5\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container view-image\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2\"><polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg></div></div></div></div></a><figcaption class=\"image-caption\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/CapsuleHeroes/status/1677029812408295431\" rel=\"\">https://twitter.com/CapsuleHeroes/status/1677029812408295431</a></figcaption></figure></div><p><span>More information in this </span><a href=\"https://endlessclouds.substack.com/p/introducing-capsule-heroes\" rel=\"\">article</a><span> and any questions you may have will be answered </span><a href=\"https://endlessclouds.substack.com/p/capsule-heroes-questions\" rel=\"\">here</a><span>. And we recommend </span><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1d06bHl2V2I\" rel=\"\">watching the trailer in good quality on YouTube</a><span>.</span></p><p>We had a lot of private demand for the physical care package we’ve been working on after I shared an image on Twitter recently with a mockup design. The updated design below is much simpler.</p><p>We have looked into pre-orders and still searching for a way to reduce the price of shipping as much as possible—but next month expect the preorders and sale!</p><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!_LqV!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fed69a7a6-af51-436b-ad98-be9e7cdf8728_3650x3041.jpeg\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\" rel=\"\" class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\"><div class=\"image2-inset\"><picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!_LqV!,w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fed69a7a6-af51-436b-ad98-be9e7cdf8728_3650x3041.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!_LqV!,w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fed69a7a6-af51-436b-ad98-be9e7cdf8728_3650x3041.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!_LqV!,w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fed69a7a6-af51-436b-ad98-be9e7cdf8728_3650x3041.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!_LqV!,w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fed69a7a6-af51-436b-ad98-be9e7cdf8728_3650x3041.jpeg 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!_LqV!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fed69a7a6-af51-436b-ad98-be9e7cdf8728_3650x3041.jpeg\" width=\"1456\" height=\"1213\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/ed69a7a6-af51-436b-ad98-be9e7cdf8728_3650x3041.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1213,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:391461,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!_LqV!,w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fed69a7a6-af51-436b-ad98-be9e7cdf8728_3650x3041.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!_LqV!,w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fed69a7a6-af51-436b-ad98-be9e7cdf8728_3650x3041.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!_LqV!,w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fed69a7a6-af51-436b-ad98-be9e7cdf8728_3650x3041.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!_LqV!,w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fed69a7a6-af51-436b-ad98-be9e7cdf8728_3650x3041.jpeg 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"sizing-normal\"></picture><div class=\"image-link-expand\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container restack-image\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-refresh-cw\"><path d=\"M3 12a9 9 0 0 1 9-9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1 6.74 2.74L21 8\"></path><path d=\"M21 3v5h-5\"></path><path d=\"M21 12a9 9 0 0 1-9 9 9.75 9.75 0 0 1-6.74-2.74L3 16\"></path><path d=\"M8 16H3v5\"></path></svg></div><div class=\"pencraft pc-reset icon-container view-image\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2\"><polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line></svg></div></div></div></div></a></figure></div><p>Last but not least, Baafi will be joining social media soon…</p><p></p><div data-component-name=\"VideoEmbedPlayer\" id=\"media-bdc6682f-8f17-4cec-abee-c91608398c42\" class=\"videoScrollTarget-SzB20Y\"><div class=\"videoPlaceholder-F7Lub5\">Could not load video.</div></div><h2 class=\"header-anchor-post\">Art Update<div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-alignItems-center pc-position-absolute pc-reset header-anchor-parent\"><div class=\"pencraft pc-display-contents pc-reset pubTheme-yiXxQA\"><div id=\"§art-update\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset header-anchor offset-top\"></div><button type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Link\" data-href=\"https://endlessclouds.substack.com/i/135568170/art-update\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft iconButton-mq_Et5 iconButtonBase-dJGHgN buttonBase-GK1x3M buttonStyle-r7yGCK size_sm-G3LciD priority_secondary-S63h9o\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-link\"><path d=\"M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71\"></path><path d=\"M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71\"></path></svg></button></div></div></h2><p><em>By Scott</em></p><p>For the month of July, we are happy to share with you some of our progress for the town of Lorwick. Below you can see the elements which we will be using to build out the entire town. Think of them like puzzle pieces, where we can rotate and combine to create a high number of unique combinations and fill out an entire environment. Building it like the image below allows us to reuse assets but still have the variety to achieve a complex and interesting space for players to quest, craft, and trade.</p><div class=\"captioned-image-container\"><figure><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!ATM3!,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%